        <header class="align-center">
            <h2>International Law</h2>
            <p>Explore the key principles and frameworks governing relations between nations.</p>
        </header>

        <p>
            International law is a system of rules established by treaty or custom that governs the relations between nations. 
            It ensures peaceful coexistence, facilitates international trade, and protects fundamental rights.
        </p>

        <p>
            Key topics include:
            <ul>
                <li>Sovereignty and State Recognition</li>
                <li>Diplomatic Relations</li>
                <li>Environmental Law</li>
                <li>Maritime Law</li>
            </ul>
        </p>

